{"tid":525581,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"D750 廣角鏡一問","createTime":"2018-01-10T20:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T04:21:52.000Z","uid":31674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c17ed15638d51dcaa9ea5a79325eda3ff67e5e","tid":525581,"uid":31674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T20:51:05.000Z","msg":"小弟想入手一支廣角鏡 有幾支心水想巴打比啲意見<br />\n<br />\nNikon 18-35 : 輕 平 成色好似麻麻 非恆定<br />\n<br />\nNikon 24-70 : 廣受好評 大光圈 恆定 二手價~7000 但好似唔夠wide<br />\n<br />\nNikon 20 f1.8 : prime lens 都多好評 輕 但冇二手 ~5500全新 MIC 但好似冇zoom lens方便 eg. 一啲景點只能特定距離觀看<br />\n<br />\nTamron 15-30 : 多人推 super-wide review聲稱直逼原廠1424 極重 大舊 冇得上filter <br />\n<br />\n比較多影景 人都會但通常幫人影 本身人支50 1.8<br />\n不直就係以上4支鏡既range<br />\n本身想入1635 但好多人都話成像不好 所以不了<br />\n希望大家比少少意見小弟"},{"pid":"b40f0b96cca03693a8d2b2fc1782b428c0014879","tid":525581,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T01:10:19.000Z","msg":"24-70可考慮Tamron 24-70 G2<br />\n(Sigma Art 24-70好垃圾）<br />\n<br />\nTamron 15-30就so far so good 啦<br />\n可以上外置filter"},{"pid":"5ef7fa40fff976dc4bf02d3efe20bafa8d32e4c1","tid":525581,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T01:17:10.000Z","msg":"2470都算？<br />\n我自己用1635又覺得ok"},{"pid":"3ba6ffb384c64f5384b26bb4ec86a7a3557bb61e","tid":525581,"uid":5143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T01:49:18.000Z","msg":"2470 standard zoom, not wide la"},{"pid":"c5f27c944c30b20595434d07af1d6e5cad50f2b0","tid":525581,"uid":31674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b40f0b96cca03693a8d2b2fc1782b428c0014879","tid":525581,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T01:10:19.000Z","msg":"24-70可考慮Tamron 24-70 G2<br />\n(Sigma Art 24-70好垃圾）<br />\n<br />\nTamron 15-30就so far so good 啦<br />\n可以上外置filter"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T03:15:55.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打建議<br />\n不過如果2470唔算wide可能就唔考慮住<br />\n唔知巴打點睇其他幾支呢<br />\n<br />\nBtw外置好撚貴<img src=\"/a